{"tid":588203,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[飲食業] 工作上嘅煩惱求開解","createTime":"2018-03-11T05:00:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-20T04:39:40.000Z","uid":24607,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7dcfb64f8336c47fb071bf6512b49db6b2bf4bdb","tid":588203,"uid":24607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T05:00:02.000Z","msg":"話說小弟讀完大學之後為咗興趣入咗廚房做嘢<br />\n因為頂唔順香港嘅廚房佬文化<br />\n兜兜轉轉去咗london嘅一間幾出名下嘅finedining度做野<br />\n用working holiday黎做嘢<br />\n本身諗住學多啲嘢上下位為目標<br />\n學到咁上下就轉工繼續學 甚至問總廚refer我去丹麥noma度做<br />\n點知今晚同總廚去飲嘢 <br />\n得知佢好睇我 未來想升我做二廚甚至大廚<br />\n仲話我visa兩年過期之後會用盡方法簽sponsorship畀我<br />\n我聽到固然開心 有少少受寵若驚<br />\n但心底其實唔想跟一個師父咁耐 <br />\n莫講話幾年 我連一年都嫌耐<br />\n但如果我周圍去下其他地方學嘢 有機會會一世做散仔<br />\n點揀好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n利申 23歲 佢升我嘅意思應該講緊一兩年嘅事"},{"pid":"88cd71c9ccbcb8d2da4f18cea8a41cd75216ca3b","tid":588203,"uid":53958,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T05:07:38.000Z","msg":"出黎做野人夾人<br />\n<br />\n你同依家D同事夾到, 大家開開心心, 人工又OK咪得囉"},{"pid":"0432de994a986ac0d87f697cf3037c145b75a74f","tid":588203,"uid":60936,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T10:18:08.000Z","msg":"總廚睇好你，又同啲同事夾到，返工開開心心咪繼續囉，周圍闖蕩唔一定係好事，但求穩定見識又增長到就得"},{"pid":"edb84bb29ccf32bcd7d57dfedea6876e0fca4780","tid":588203,"uid":24607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"88cd71c9ccbcb8d2da4f18cea8a41cd75216ca3b","tid":588203,"uid":53958,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T05:07:38.000Z","msg":"出黎做野人夾人<br />\n<br />\n你同依家D同事夾到, 大家開開心心, 人工又OK咪得囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T13:07:32.000Z","msg":"同事呢家嘢 走下黎下好快就成班唔同晒<br />\n廚房流失率好高<br />\n至於人工 暫時唔係我考慮因素<br />\n而且本身我讀完可以做教書慢慢加人工<br />\n但而家𢭃得嗰萬八 仲要一日做16個鐘 返四日半<br />\n可能去到其他地方都係差唔遠<br />\n但真係想學多啲唔同風格嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73532eeef3b6059ccd2bbf9a775bf3c09658db4a","tid":588203,"uid":39608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T13:11:26.000Z","msg":"成一兩年後既事咁快煩惱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話唔定幾個月後你有新諗法又或者總廚都過左檔呢"},{"pid":"9581bd2bb39743dd0295ddcd6db58e1120d1eec5","tid":588203,"uid":24607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73532eeef3b6059ccd2bbf9a775bf3c09658db4a","tid":588203,"uid":39608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T13:11:26.000Z","msg":"成一兩年後既事咁快煩惱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話唔定幾個月後你有新諗法又或者總廚都過左檔呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T13:15:54.000Z","msg":"本身我諗住做多幾個月辭職<br />\n返香港一陣又好 喺英國搵第間又好<br />\n本身冇諗過要做多過一年 太辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n總廚叫我唔好同大廚講其實佢搵緊第二間餐廳做<br />\n過多一年就會轉 然後佢講到明叫我跟佢過去<br />\n好糾結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e82491f9d382993f4e8a588cea81d94df3c244be","tid":588203,"uid":24607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T13:38:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f57e421ca606b192c5c81783076a3f20bbcaee3c","tid":588203,"uid":146538,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T14:15:48.000Z","msg":"捱多陣上咗位再走同你而家散仔身份走好唔同<br />\n散仔走將來都只不過係同人講做咗幾耐散仔<br />\n2/大廚出黎將來都可以直接應徵返相應職位<br />\n你只不過係年少氣盛個心定唔到<br />\n你心底裡都知道留多陣係更好"},{"pid":"4b2855fc05f6beb081507af571f8433937f7491f","tid":588203,"uid":24607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f57e421ca606b192c5c81783076a3f20bbcaee3c","tid":588203,"uid":146538,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T14:15:48.000Z","msg":"捱多陣上咗位再走同你而家散仔身份走好唔同<br />\n散仔走將來都只不過係同人講做咗幾耐散仔<br />\n2/大廚出黎將來都可以直接應徵返相應職位<br />\n你只不過係年少氣盛個心定唔到<br />\n你心底裡都知道留多陣係更好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T15:58:18.000Z","msg":"你講得啱 其實我自己都知留喺度上位係最好<br />\n但真係好想去見識下學多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4551aef2fbbf9d4e85da29f5bbb014e30042a0a6","tid":588203,"uid":9253,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T16:55:20.000Z","msg":"我覺得你係到再學下野先 就咁就出左去 你第時一定後悔 <br />\n你跳左出去，你唔知人地係咪真係會比機會係學野，你留係到起碼有得升 有個大佬會教你野 <br />\n你咪升到咁上下有番咁上下經驗再跳出去囉 你家下先23 過多2-3年再轉出去未嘗一件壞事"},{"pid":"8b5408c270166ff90409c86b5446f5a834551a74","tid":588203,"uid":119979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T17:01:43.000Z","msg":"你簽sponsorship好似至少5年contract"},{"pid":"c16ab302bacddc2a3e2b5171e3ef6693e5ed7371","tid":588203,"uid":160833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T17:18:25.000Z","msg":"有得發展 何樂以不為？ 你流浪mode幾時都可以 機會唔係成日有"},{"pid":"1555dde5dd666e985b4d9e2eccc252e2406102d4","tid":588203,"uid":24607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4551aef2fbbf9d4e85da29f5bbb014e30042a0a6","tid":588203,"uid":9253,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T16:55:20.000Z","msg":"我覺得你係到再學下野先 就咁就出左去 你第時一定後悔 <br />\n你跳左出去，你唔知人地係咪真係會比機會係學野，你留係到起碼有得升 有個大佬會教你野 <br />\n你咪升到咁上下有番咁上下經驗再跳出去囉 你家下先23 過多2-3年再轉出去未嘗一件壞事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T00:21:53.000Z","msg":"唉 個心態好急進 <br />\n因為做廚師真係冇生活可言<br />\n我一個禮拜先打到一次電話返屋企<br />\n好想快啲捱完呢個階段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除非做啲普通餐廳 會有多啲私人時間<br />\n但始終都係鍾意做finedining<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0720517a121f1fbf1702a9d27ca69e2334af753","tid":588203,"uid":24607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c16ab302bacddc2a3e2b5171e3ef6693e5ed7371","tid":588203,"uid":160833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T17:18:25.000Z","msg":"有得發展 何樂以不為？ 你流浪mode幾時都可以 機會唔係成日有"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T00:23:36.000Z","msg":"因為我真係好想去noma度做<br />\n直頭係我夢想黎<br />\n本身一心諗住可以靠個exechef介紹我入去<br />\n但我諗佢唔會咁大方掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69c4646187f69d70e42b97e429578b32827a23e6","tid":588203,"uid":66099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1555dde5dd666e985b4d9e2eccc252e2406102d4","tid":588203,"uid":24607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4551aef2fbbf9d4e85da29f5bbb014e30042a0a6","tid":588203,"uid":9253,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T16:55:20.000Z","msg":"我覺得你係到再學下野先 就咁就出左去 你第時一定後悔 <br />\n你跳左出去，你唔知人地係咪真係會比機會係學野，你留係到起碼有得升 有個大佬會教你野 <br />\n你咪升到咁上下有番咁上下經驗再跳出去囉 你家下先23 過多2-3年再轉出去未嘗一件壞事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T00:21:53.000Z","msg":"唉 個心態好急進 <br />\n因為做廚師真係冇生活可言<br />\n我一個禮拜先打到一次電話返屋企<br />\n好想快啲捱完呢個階段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除非做啲普通餐廳 會有多啲私人時間<br />\n但始終都係鍾意做finedining<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T00:24:45.000Z","msg":"working holiday 點揾到廚房？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a2ae177dc2973bcc84d3a5eeeea6ded41d3a52c","tid":588203,"uid":24607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b5408c270166ff90409c86b5446f5a834551a74","tid":588203,"uid":119979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T17:01:43.000Z","msg":"你簽sponsorship好似至少5年contract"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T00:25:03.000Z","msg":"好似唔關事<br />\n我都唔清楚 冇研究"},{"pid":"74c01c09aa7a0e476ccc00305d69feb96dd432eb","tid":588203,"uid":24607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69c4646187f69d70e42b97e429578b32827a23e6","tid":588203,"uid":66099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1555dde5dd666e985b4d9e2eccc252e2406102d4","tid":588203,"uid":24607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4551aef2fbbf9d4e85da29f5bbb014e30042a0a6",